3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper discusses the use of string kernels in various text classification tasks, which is relevant to information retrieval. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a machine learning algorithm for text classification, which is a subfield of AI.
